# Microsoft Fabric Implementation

## Fabric Components

- Eventhouse: `eh_stm_realtime`
- KQL Database: `kqldb_stm_operations`
- Eventstreams: `evs_stm_transit_events`, `evs_stm_service_status`
- Lakehouse: `lh_stm_transit`
- Pipelines: scheduled collection workflows
- Semantic Model: `sem_stm_transit_operations`
- Dashboard: `STM Transit Intelligence Dashboard`

## Processing Layers

- Bronze: raw ingestion
- Silver: cleaned transit entities
- Gold: operational KPIs and map-ready outputs

## Why Fabric

Microsoft Fabric provides one environment for real-time ingestion, KQL analytics, Lakehouse processing, semantic modeling, and dashboarding.
